question.en:
Given this GraphQL code snippet:

query GetUser {
  user(id: "1") {
    name
    email
  }
}

mutation UpdateUser {
  updateUser(id: "1", name: "John") {
    name
    email
  }
}

subscription OnUserChanged {
  userChanged(id: "1") {
    name
  }
}

Which statement best describes the intended use of each operation?

